{
  "stem": "8252.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I remember that some people were-- had gold on them and to just get on a wagon, driven by a peasant going the same way took gold and, and jewelry and so on.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But anyhow, we were walking like that for about three days, through at night-- through nights and so on of very bad bombing and shooting at us from the planes.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And just before we got to Warsaw-- maybe 10, 15 miles from Warsaw, from the suburbs of Warsaw-- there was a bombing raid again, and they were machine gunning the people that were walking towards Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I jumped into a ditch next to the road and all of a sudden we hear a racket, a big noise on, on the road.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I say, my God, why the Polish trucks are going with the-- with the army?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why are they making so much noise?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We'll be bombed for much longer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And somebody looks ahead and says, they are not Polish trucks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They are German motorcycles.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's my first encounter with the German army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as I was sitting there, a, a power that I, I just couldn't believe it existed-- motorized power just passed in front of my eyes.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At this time, of course, we didn't know much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It wasn't the same power as now, but seeing all these motorized troops was a tremendous impression on me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we started going back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We started going back because there was no, no way we could go forward to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Warsaw was surrounded at that point.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I came back to my city of Lodz, oh, around the 10th of September, maybe, maybe, maybe 12th, something like that.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as I said, I was sleeping that time at my sister's-- in my sister's apartment.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
